18 |title=The Fiend in Gray |first=Jane|last=Singer |date=2003-06-01 |work=[[The Washington Post]] |accessdate=2010-12-09}} *{{cite journal|ref=harv |title=review of ''The Confederate Dirty War: Arson, Bombings, Assassination, and Plots for Chemical and Germ Attacks on the Union'' |first=Jonathan M.|last=Williams |journal=Military Review |date=May–June 2006 |url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m0PBZ/is_3_86/ai_n16533294/|accessdate=2010-12-08}} {{refend}}
